Q1.Populate ticket_created_at column in feedbacks table using created_at from ticket table

Solution:

Using  INDEX& Match  to fetch the created_at value from the ticket sheet

Formula:
=INDEX(Sheet1!B:B,MATCH(A3,Sheet1!E:E,0))

Explanation:
A3 → cms_id in your feedback sheet
Sheet1!E:E → cms_id column in ticket sheet
MATCH(A3,Sheet1!E:E,0) → finds the row number of that cms_id
INDEX(Sheet1!B:B, … ) → returns the created_at value from column B


This formula fills the ticket_created_at column
