Q2.Fetch outlet-wise count of tickets created and closed

a) Closed on same day

Creating  a new column in ticket sheet

Formula:
=IF(DATE(created_at)=DATE(closed_at),"Same Day","No")

Then using  Pivot Table

Steps:
Select ticket data
Click Insert → Pivot Table
Add outlet_id → Rows
Add ticket_id → Values (Count)
Filter Same Day
-----------------------------
b)Closed in same hour

Creating  another column

Formula:
=IF(HOUR(created_at)=HOUR(closed_at),"Same Hour","No")

Then using  Pivot Table again to count tickets per outlet.
